 Galvatron saw  Quilldart jet towards the base. "Good no doubt the other two 
are not far behind." He sent a comm to Rodimus. A holographic image of 
himself would display. "I am so glad Rodimus we could come to terms. As for 
our one on one battle. Dont you worry. That will happen in due time. Until 
then best of luck my old friend. I havent had this much fun since our little 
unicron adventure...wouldnt you agree?" He ended the comm and turned back to 
the map. He had his three blips on the screen. 

--part1_da.1c3e1430.2a8af2ef_boundary
